|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| Unroll/Inline |                             |              | After user unroll and inline pragmas are applied                                       |
|               | (1) unroll                  | 34,182       | user unroll pragmas are applied                                                        |
|               | (2) simplification          | 11,590       | simplification of applied user unroll pragmas                                          |
