|               | (4) simplification          | 10,422       | simplification of applied user inline pragmas                                          |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| Array/Struct  |                             |              | After user array partition and struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas are applied       |
|               | (1) array partition         |  4,069       | user array partition pragmas are applied                                               |
|               | (2) simplification          |  2,970       | simplification of applied user array partition & struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas |
|               | (3) aggregate/disaggregate  |  2,982       | user struct aggregate/disaggregate pragmas are applied                                 |
|               | (4) array reshape           |  3,858       | apply array reshape pragmas                                                            |
|               | (5) access patterns         |  3,853       | array access pattern optmizations                                                      |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| Performance   |                             |              | After transformations are applied to meet performance pragma targets                   |
|               | (1) loop simplification     |  3,805       | loop and instruction simplification                                                    |
|               | (2) parallelization         |  3,803       | loops are unrolled or pipelined to meet performance targets                            |
|               | (3) array partition         |  3,817       | arrays are partitioned to meet performance targets                                     |
|               | (4) simplification          |  3,817       | simplification of design after performance transformations                             |
|               |                             |              |                                                                                        |
| HW Transforms |                             |              | After hardware transfomations                                                          |
|               | (1) lowering                |  3,616       | initial conversion to HW specific instructions                                         |
|               | (2) optimizations           |  3,621       | high level synthesis optimizations                                                     |
